{"lastUpdated":"2026-06-16T19:53:22.776Z","seriesId":109113,"title":"Soul Link","thumbnailUrl":"https://nicovideo.cdn.nimg.jp/thumbnails/36383986/36383986.77611981","descriptionFirst":"西暦2045年。宇宙研修のため、衛星軌道上のステーションホテル「アリエス」に到着した中央士官学校予科の生徒達。予科3年所属「相澤涼太」は、厳しい訓練と寮生活とは違う宇宙体験にドキドキだった。そして数日後、1通のメッセージが届く。それは尊敬する兄「相澤秀平」が本科研修でアリエスにくるというもので…。\n\n相澤涼太:荻原秀樹／永瀬沙佳:増田ゆき／相澤秀平:伊藤健太郎／森崎七央:佐久間紅美／新田亜希:大野まりな／ユウ＝ヤマナミ:嶋方淳子 他\n\n原作:Navel／キャラクター原案:鈴平ひろ／監督・シリーズ構成:所俊克／脚本:長谷川勝己、静谷伊佐夫／キャラクターデザイン:渡辺義弘／総作画監督:渡辺義弘、早川ナオミ／美術監督:宮前光春／色彩設計:のぼりはるこ／アニメーション制作:ピクチャーマジック\n\n©Omegavision,Inc.／Soul Link Media Project 2006\n\n次話→so36384010","tags":["アニメ","第一話","2006年春アニメ","エロゲ・エロアニメ原作","SF/ファンタジー"],"cours":"2006-春","colKey":"さ","relatedSeries":[],"episodes":[{"contentId":"so36383986","episodeNo":1,"title":"Soul Link　第1話　ENCOUNTER －出会い－","viewCounter":940,"startTime":"2021-12-10T10:00:00+09:00","thumbnailUrl":"https://nicovideo.cdn.nimg.jp/thumbnails/36383986/36383986.77611981"},{"contentId":"so36384010","episodeNo":2,"title":"Soul Link　第2話　CONTACT －接触－","viewCounter":217,"startTime":"2021-12-10T10:00:00+09:00","thumbnailUrl":"https://nicovideo.cdn.nimg.jp/thumbnails/36384010/36384010.50817111"},{"contentId":"so36384030","episodeNo":3,"title":"Soul Link　第3話　OUTBREAK －勃発－","viewCounter":663,"startTime":"2021-12-10T10:00:00+09:00","thumbnailUrl":"https://nicovideo.cdn.nimg.jp/thumbnails/36384030/36384030.77858733"},{"contentId":"so36384072","episodeNo":4,"title":"Soul Link　第4話　BREATHING SPACE －休息－","viewCounter":176,"startTime":"2021-12-10T10:00:00+09:00","thumbnailUrl":"https://nicovideo.cdn.nimg.jp/thumbnails/36384072/36384072.22922290"},{"contentId":"so36384131","episodeNo":5,"title":"Soul Link　第5話　WATERSHED －分岐点－","viewCounter":167,"startTime":"2021-12-10T10:00:00+09:00","thumbnailUrl":"https://nicovideo.cdn.nimg.jp/thumbnails/36384131/36384131.14186418"},{"contentId":"so36384132","episodeNo":6,"title":"Soul Link　第6話　FAREWELL －別れ－","viewCounter":240,"startTime":"2021-12-10T10:00:00+09:00","thumbnailUrl":"http